  "siteName": "随机小分队",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\">\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <div style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\">\n      <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:10px 0px 16px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-powered-by&quot;:&quot;yiban.io&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, \\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;output&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding-left: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: 26px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, \\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; white-space: pre-line; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;word-break: break-all; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Product Hunt是全球最流行的发掘有意思新产品的平台。</span>经过近十年的发展，已经成为用户发现新产品、创业者获得灵感、投资人寻找新机会，以及创始人对产品进行推广的最好地方。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">上一期的 Product Hunt 月榜中，华人团队强势霸榜，我们也在</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NTAwMzU1MA==&amp;mid=2247504440&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8b1612f9be7a54acf32c5be9f9ebaab4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"ProductHunt月榜快被华人“占满”了\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">ProductHunt月榜快被华人“占满”了</a></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">文章中进行过报道；而本次却只剩下 Xmind 一家华人团队上榜，他们在上个月发布了一款轻量的任务管理工具。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">本期的月榜中，ChatGPT 最新发布的 AI 浏览器和 Cursor 的最新版本纷纷上榜，此外还有关于视频协作、自动化、AI 编程等方向的多款工具。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">话不多说，下面就请来具体看看本期有趣的产品。</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">1.Flask：AI视频制作工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频创作团队在协作过程中，沟通效率低下、创意难以准确表达，传统工具不够直观。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Flask 主要面向视频创作及团队协作场景，核心功能包括：在线视频协作、无限评论与录屏、AI 智能洞察、团队共享空间、版本管理、支持多素材上传等。其特色在于以视频为核心的创意交流方式，他强调自己是“Notion+Loom”，可以通过视频形式给予反馈，还可加各种 Tag 跟踪进度，极大提升了反馈的直观性和协作乐趣。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为一款视频制作工具，Flask 在官网首页制作的产品介绍视频质量很高，创始人出镜将产品特点讲述的非常清晰，值得大家参考。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020832\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f2da44e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8AtcTyGK68voz481bY4hC0hXUoVWwPCAWrYB60b9ia5SzzXgPWYsEUnJNSV3zbBCoTpA4mNs9eM9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Flask 提供免费版本；付费版定价为 13 美元/月，团队共享空间、多版本管理、去除品牌标识等高级功能。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：752</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：flask.do</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">2.Project Management by Xmind：轻量级项目管理工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Xmind 一直是华人出海的标杆企业，这次他们又推出了自己的项目管理工具。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Project Management by Xmind 专注于早期项目规划与执行的无缝衔接，适用于头脑风暴、任务分解和轻量级项目管理场景。其核心功能包括将思维导图节点转化为带日期、优先级和进度的任务，支持实时协作、切换不同结构（如组织图、时间线）进行任务分解，以及通过甘特图直观跟踪项目进展。当然，Xmind 一如既往的保持了它优秀的设计风格，UI 让人赏心悦目。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100020833\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" style=\"pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=51038a9f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8AtcTyGK68voz481bY4hC0udRj2sFUCNGa4wQbI5JJcibgAFofIP4GviaRgMYiaSZs0WTRyv5egTleA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Project Management by Xmind 提供免费版本；付费版定价为 10-15 美元/月，包含导出、实时协作、AI任务分解、甘特图、任务分配等功能。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：614</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：xmind.com</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">3.Director：网页自动化工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">许多复杂的在线任务需要重复的手动操作，例如点击、填写表单、导航网页和提取数据，这些任务耗时且容易出错。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Director 是一款基于 AI 的网页自动化工具，适用于需要重复性操作、数据提取和流程自动化的场景。用户只需通过自然语言提示，即可生成自动化工作流，Director 的虚拟浏览器能够模拟人工操作，包括点击按钮、填写表单、登录账户及提取数据。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100020834\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" style=\"pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bc34c657&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8AtcTyGK68voz481bY4hC0t32BjbIY4krckUFx7SaL8PNnZFwTVCWGXMAqUhf5vO7bz138U28XDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Director 目前提供免费版本。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：686</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：director.ai</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">4.Orchids：AI 全栈工程师工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在构建应用和网站时，往往会遇到技术门槛高、开发周期长以及整合前后端、数据库、认证和支付等问题。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Orchids 是一款 AI 全栈工程师工具，专注于简化应用和网站的开发流程。用户通过与 AI 聊天即可完成从前端、后端到数据库、认证和支付的全栈开发，无需依赖任何第三方集成工具。他的核心功能包括快速实现完整的技术栈、支持部署网站、网站分析及自定义域名等，特色功能还包括代码库下载和实时优先支持，帮助用户高效构建和迭代项目。</span></p>\n        <p nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi4a5hpvw2n\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020823\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6094182825484764\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"722\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;background-color: transparent;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b1eaa65&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FfFKE45D7xm8AtcTyGK68voz481bY4hC0AuP9IREqCWTYO488oDoxVF9AnDdmoticM8DTpyERb99u5aarSe1CicicA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;