-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：566</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：mynora.ai</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">9.Caesr AI：跨平台的 AI 自动化工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在实际工作中，用户经常需要在复杂界面、过时软件或无 API 支持的环境中完成自动化任务，而现有的自动化工具通常只能在理想条件下运行，难以应对这些情况。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Caesr AI 是一款跨平台的 AI 自动化工具，用户需先下载安装 macOS 或 Windows 的桌面端软件，之后只需通过自然语言描述，即可通过其实现点击、输入、表单填写、测试运行等操作，无需编写脚本或集成 API，这种模式大幅扩展了自动化工作流的适用场景。</span></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\"></figure>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020827\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d6f91d55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8AtcTyGK68voz481bY4hC0vNFT0RaVFrLOz8HpoicaoFsNua6zicYce0E4sG6Wt08qicsXXib3LUEenw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\"></figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Caesr 提供免费版本，包含 500 积分；付费版定价为 29 欧元/月起，按用量付费。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：550</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：caesr.ai</span></p>\n        <h3 style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">10.v0 for iOS：移动端开发工具</span></span></h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在全栈应用开发中，开发者常面临从设计到部署的协作效率低下、跨平台操作繁琐以及工具整合困难的问题，特别是在移动端缺乏实用工具。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">v0 for iOS 是一款由 Vercel 提供的协作式 AI 助手，专为设计、迭代和扩展全栈应用而打造。其核心功能包括通过 iPhone 实现应用设计与部署、可视化编辑、与 GitHub 同步，以及从 Figma 导入设计文件。用户只需通过简单的提示，即可完成从创意到部署的全过程，随时随地提升开发效率。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100020828\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5626598465473146\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"782\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f9c6d72c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FfFKE45D7xm8AtcTyGK68voz481bY4hC0GDbf5tp0hjnarxiaLGKBPNDwepaOaPVNbVLRLib4FicGdsCF99NnN29zA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n        <figure style=\"margin-top: 0px;\"></figure>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">v0 提供免费版本；付费版定价为20美元/月，包含更高附件大小限制、Figma 导入等高级功能。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：645</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：v0.app</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
